cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with pedestrian detection. It also involves training a robust classifier and an accurate box regressor, which are common tasks in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper introduces a new box sign predictor, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and computer security (cs.CR) sub-categories.
